; Regression test for issue #606: Padding formatting commands does not ignore invisible characters (BZ#606)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/606
;
; The bug: justify() counts invisible ANSI escape codes toward the padding width,
; resulting in less padding than expected (visible text not reaching target width).

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(justify(ansify_if(account, "red", true), 25)) %(amount)\n'
[31mExpenses:Food[0m        $10.00
[31mAssets:Cash[0m          $-10.00
end test
